<D>__{dad used to bring home these sparklers to me and adam. out back we'd light 'em up. the three of us. we'd hold 'em up to the sky and watch the explosions of light. sparks. and dad would be all... "get ready"... "watch for it"... "here it comes," here comes the "wahoo"}
<C>__{fisher}
<D>__{the wahoo?}
