<D>__{the sparkler would burn hot, then hotter, then even hotter... and there would be one moment of pure burn when that little fucker would cook just perfect. perfect. it would only last a second, but that second was it. it was it. that's what dad had us looking for... you get me?}
<C>__{fisher}
<D>__{the wahoo moment?}
